Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:45.42,ED_JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{an2}{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,8780,8980)}何でもなく 笑いあった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:45.30,Default - Style 00,,0,0,0,,Nan de mo naku waraiatta
